{"tid":1617313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"整左個APP可以幫到大家知道附近發生緊乜事","createTime":"2019-10-03T17:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T01:46:19.000Z","uid":329631,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db7390338fde33e3524a8ff525205d35213101d1","tid":1617313,"uid":329631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:28:12.000Z","msg":"小弟啱啱寫左好個APP可以俾大家分享所在地發生緊乜事，等我介紹下俾大家，睇下大家啱唔啱用<br />\n貼左條LINK先：（暫時只有iOS版本）<br />\n<a href=\"https://SkyReal.app/Download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2FSkyReal.app%2FDownload%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=046b23b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://SkyReal.app/Download/</a><br />\n<br />\n用法好簡單，以下係教學：<br />\n<strong>1. 登記</strong><br />\n裝左個APP之後，禁Get started, Register 個 Account <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNZ5DUm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNZ5DUm.png&h=26c8120e&s={SIZE}\" /> \u0018 <br />\n打EMAIL同密碼就OK<br />\n\u0016<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2W2ZJmh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2W2ZJmh.png&h=53db6a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後你會收到封EMAIL，禁條LINK就OK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMO6ona.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMO6ona.png&h=6dd74111&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n番番去APP，禁 Got account? Sign in here<br />\n打番EMAIL同PASSWORD就OK<br />\n<br />\n第一次登入係會要可以UPLOAD相，打username, 性別同介紹下自己（之後可以改）<br />\n跟住要揀你想睇的類別，一開始我幫你揀晒，你唔要可以OFF左佢（之後可以改）<br />\n我特登整左個Special Tag - 🇭🇰 Hong Kong Protest係最底，大家可以用啲個CATEGORY開POST去SHARE Hong Kong Protest的POST去討論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvJFsUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvJFsUK.png&h=3eaccbfc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後要開LOCATION，主要用黎SCAN你附近有乜POST同開POST用<br />\nNotification, 開左先，個功能未有時間整<br />\n<br />\n話咁快就搞掂～<br />\n<br />\n一入到去，如果你果區無人之前POST過嘢，咁你可以直接睇&quot;2. 開POST&quot;去開個POST玩玩先<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 開POST</strong><br />\n開POST我盡量想簡單化佢，你禁右上角個&quot;＋&quot;制<br />\n咁佢會彈個MAP出黎，有個教學係右上角，但我諗你睇完都唔知我講乜，跟我做一次最實際<br />\n中間條BAR 可以拉上拉下，但iOS 13 壞左。。。遲啲整<br />\n重點黎啦，最底果個部份，你係有機會乜都見唔到，見到好簡單，你㨂個啱的地方就OK，好似啲個例子咁，你見有IFC，你揀IFC，咁啲人如果係IFC附近就會見到個POST<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEGDeB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEGDeB5.png&h=53af2f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁但係如果你見唔到嘢係最底，或者無你鍾意的地方咁點？<br />\n禁個MAP啲ICON！<br />\nICON有就盡量禁，咁會ACCURATE啲去話俾人聽你個地方，無都唔緊要，揀個最相關的 <br />\n例如，如果你係其中一間IFC的餐廳，但個MAP又搵唔到佢個ICON ，你可以直接揀IFC就OK<br />\n<br />\n咁揀完位置就打嘢，乜都無所謂，我唔會DELETE你，但唔好SPAM我，打啲有意義的嘢，你可以罵間餐廳話佢好難食（Food），又可以同人CHITCHAT（BupBup），可以叫人幫手，因為一陣你可以揀個CATEGORY<br />\n如果想貼相，係得GEI！但係我自己整的比較廢啲，要一張一張咁貼，遲啲先ENHANCE<br />\n<br />\n打完會變左咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jkpxi7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjkpxi7n.png&h=5d9b8ee3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁CATEGORY，你揀番個啱的就OK<br />\n<br />\n記住，PUBLISH左就無得改架啦，所有嘢OK就咁PUBLISH<br />\n<br />\nREFRESH一下，就會見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvADY7Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvADY7Y.png&h=9d56ad84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日打住咁多先。。<br />\n<br />\n之後啲幾日再打埋點FILTER啲POST，點睇POST，點留言，點SEARCH TAG，點睇自己PROFILE<br />\n<br />\n如果有乜BUG或者可以改善的地方，麻煩大家俾俾意見🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n如果個APP OK，可以介紹朋友都用，愈多人 SHARE INFORMATION 愈有用<br />\n或者都可以俾個FB LIKE 等我開心下： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SkyRealChat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSkyRealChat%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=35649f01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SkyRealChat/</a><br />\n或者IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/skyrealchat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fskyrealchat%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=0366572b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/skyrealchat/</a><br />\n<br />\n有乜問題可以留言或者send email 俾我 admin@SkyReal.com"},{"pid":"a35e89833fddbf956c462a06b5513e5429d04e84","tid":1617313,"uid":59151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"推 即刻試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9726689c2b2248e9bdd80df5f5c4ce2efa5f4182","tid":1617313,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"de863a111fd37cb637b28f5b450e9d116d999c04","tid":1617313,"uid":329631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e7ae01767f924b0325354b2e9b177d60fc6b05","tid":1617313,"uid":263150,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:33:16.000Z","msg":"點先知作者唔係警方？"},{"pid":"3bd86242a056ddd393ef356c1be060accdb39fa0","tid":1617313,"uid":47850,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"好有可疑！！！<br />\n<br />\n其他我唔敢講，但大家嘅email address樓主一定會攞到<br />\n<br />\n請問樓主咩背景？"},{"pid":"3916d7cc32e324ea163cd9a7bb77210044a46bc5","tid":1617313,"uid":63392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"點解一定要email address 登記？"},{"pid":"e0e92365bf0ffac7b11ca14e866abe1b96931aef","tid":1617313,"uid":329631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:39:22.000Z","msg":"三十歲，IT人，用左幾年時間工餘時間寫，原意係想俾人同身邊的人share身邊的事吖"},{"pid":"30f4c03fc56335368c93952111136b5412fbc6d1","tid":1617313,"uid":329266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"係呢個狗攞人電話上連登，又涉及私隱既年代&hellip;<br />\n樓主會唔會考慮下其他更保障個人私隱既方法？"},{"pid":"ca64a26f0d9cc1bb69cffe9d61cef325fa83e51e","tid":1617313,"uid":329631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3916d7cc32e324ea163cd9a7bb77210044a46bc5","tid":1617313,"uid":63